{:title=>"Adaptive teaching", :slug=>"adaptive-teaching", :breadcrumbs=>[{:text=>"Home", :url=>"/"}, {:text=>"Hiring and development", :url=>"/category/hiring"}, {:text=>"Supporting early career teachers", :url=>"/sub-category/supporting-early-career-teachers"}], :last_updated=>"2019-06-26", :contents_list=>[{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Principles to learn", :type=>:internal, :url=>"#what-a-newly-qualified-teacher-(nqt)-needs-to-learn"}}, {:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Skills to develop", :type=>:internal, :url=>"#what-skills-an-nqt-needs-to-develop"}}, {:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Resources", :type=>:internal, :url=>"#resources"}}, {:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Case studies", :type=>:internal, :url=>"#case-studies"}}], :content=>[{:type=>:image, :data=>{:url=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/39APdN7OS30U4GzAG5WfNb/0252dbdf1b6160ec70edc224cdefd581/53224219_1489256524541522_4335915866861461131_n.jpg", :width=>"default"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l\" id=\"what-a-newly-qualified-teacher-(nqt)-needs-to-learn\">What a newly qualified teacher (NQT) needs to learn</h2>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">There are 7 areas an NQT needs to understand and gain experience in.</p>"}}, {:type=>:bullet_list, :data=>{:name=>"Adaptive teaching > What a newly qualified teacher (NQT) needs to learn", :type=>:ordered, :large_numbers=>true, :items=>[{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"understanding-how-pupils-learn-at-different-speeds\"><b>Understanding how pupils learn at different speeds</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">Pupils learn at different rates. Recognising the varying speeds at which pupils learn, and the different types of help they need, will help NQTs create a supportive learning environment.</p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"appreciating-the-differences-between-pupils\"><b>Appreciating the differences between pupils</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">Some pupils will have prior knowledge of subjects, others will have barriers that need to be overcome before they can learn. NQTs should take differences between pupils into account when preparing lessons.</p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"giving-struggling-pupils-special-attention\"><b>Giving struggling pupils special attention</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">Where pupils are struggling, NQTs should be responsive and adapt lessons so they provide targeted support for those who need extra help to succeed.</p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"creating-and-monitoring-learning-groups\"><b>Creating and monitoring learning groups</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">NQTs should organise pupils into flexible groups to give support to those who need it most. Closely monitoring these groups will allow NQTs to spot any impacts on engagement or motivation, and swop groups around if necessary.</p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"treating-groups-of-pupils-the-same\"><b>Treating groups of pupils the same</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">If groups of pupils are given different tasks to complete, it can lower expectations for some students. NQTs should give all pupils the same tasks, and give extra support to any groups of students who are struggling.</p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"planning-lessons-without-worrying-about-learning-styles\"><b>Planning lessons without worrying about learning styles</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">There&#39;s no evidence to suggest that pupils have different learning styles. NQTs should focus on developing lessons that address the needs of pupils, rather than trying to tailor them to different styles of learning.</p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"focusing-on-pupils-with-special-needs\"><b>Focusing on pupils with special needs</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">Pupils with special educational needs or disabilities may require more support. NQTs should work closely with colleagues, families and pupils to understand and tackle any barriers to learning.</p>"}}]}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<hr />\n<p class=\"govuk-body\"></p>"}}, {:type=>:image, :data=>{:url=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/ovRi4dHWkCsPJq3UDoDlQ/bc8b48a8a30db574da6ad9787ed33282/standard_4b.png", :width=>"default"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l\" id=\"what-skills-an-nqt-needs-to-develop\">What skills an NQT needs to develop</h2>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">To help NQTs succeed, mentors should dedicate time to sharing their experience of:</p>\n<ul class=\"govuk-list govuk-list--bullet\"><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">identifying pupils who need extra help</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">adapting lessons to support pupils with different needs</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">developing lessons that create a positive learning environment for the whole class</p></li></ul>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">A mentor needs to help NQTs know how to:</p>\n<ul class=\"govuk-list govuk-list--bullet\"><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">understand the needs of different pupils</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">allow all pupils to experience success</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">support individual needs without creating unnecessary work</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">put pupils into flexible groups to aid learning</p></li></ul>\n<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"understanding-different-pupil-needs\"><b>Understanding different pupil needs</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">An NQT needs to be able to:</p>\n<ul class=\"govuk-list govuk-list--bullet\"><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">spot pupils who would benefit from breaking down lessons into smaller chunks that are easier to understand</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">use formative assessment to help NQTs modify their teaching and help improve learning</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">work with special education and safeguarding leads to work out which pupils need attention</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">use the SEND code of practice for guidance when deciding which pupils would benefit from additional support</p></li></ul>\n<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"the-importance-of-experiencing-success\"><b>The importance of experiencing success</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">An NQT needs to be able to:</p>\n<ul class=\"govuk-list govuk-list--bullet\"><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">adapt lessons so that all pupils have a chance to experience success while maintaining high expectations</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">slowly introduce new content in lessons, so that all pupils have a chance to understand important concepts</p></li></ul>\n<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"meeting-individual-needs-without-unnecessary-workload\"><b>Meeting individual needs without unnecessary workload</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">An NQT needs to be able to:</p>\n<ul class=\"govuk-list govuk-list--bullet\"><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">make best use of all resources available to them, including textbooks</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">address knowledge gaps first to connect with pupils&#39; existing knowledge if pupils lack critical knowledge before NQTs introduce new content</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">frame questions in such a way that pupils understand the question and can draw on their existing knowledge</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">consider if it&#39;s more efficient to work with struggling pupils in small groups as part of lessons, or to arrange special lessons for these pupils another time</p></li></ul>\n<h3 class=\"govuk-heading-m\" id=\"grouping-pupils\"><b>Grouping pupils</b></h3>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\">An NQT needs to be able to:</p>\n<ul class=\"govuk-list govuk-list--bullet\"><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">have high expectations for all groups of pupils and offer a rich curriculum</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">change groups regularly so that pupils don&#39;t think these groups are fixed</p></li><li><p class=\"govuk-body\">ensure groups are subject specific when they are based on attainment </p></li></ul>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\"></p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<hr />\n<p class=\"govuk-body\"></p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l\" id=\"resources\">Resources</h2>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\"></p>"}}, {:type=>:columns, :data=>{:columns=>[[{:type=>:image_link_with_description, :data=>{:image_src=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/5wHsbloA3EUWuWUaOQpAF3/2ab2d1db2d3b91945f9c1c0880853273/resource-standard-5.png", :link=>{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Making effective use of teaching assistants", :type=>:internal, :url=>"/resource/making-effective-use-of-teaching-assistants"}}, :description=>{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<p class=\"govuk-body\"><a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"/resource/making-effective-use-of-teaching-assistants\">Making effective use of teaching assistants</a></p>"}}}}], [{:type=>:paragraph, :data=>{:text=>" ", :alignment=>"left"}}]]}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<hr />\n<p class=\"govuk-body\"></p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l\" id=\"case-studies\">Case studies</h2>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\"></p>"}}, {:type=>:columns, :data=>{:columns=>[[{:type=>:image_link_with_description, :data=>{:image_src=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/cBtx1rtnplkk9YyZjQ0WA/c7dbe77160cd879cebc05e20fdfa8778/laptop.jpg", :link=>{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Using technology to aid school improvement", :type=>:internal, :url=>"/case-study/using-technology-to-aid-school-improvement"}}, :description=>{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<p class=\"govuk-body\"><a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"/case-study/using-technology-to-aid-school-improvement\">Using technology to aid school improvement</a></p>"}}}}], [{:type=>:paragraph, :data=>{:text=>" ", :alignment=>"left"}}]]}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<hr />\n<p class=\"govuk-body\"></p>"}}, {:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<h2 class=\"govuk-heading-l\" id=\"standards\">Standards</h2>\n<p class=\"govuk-body\"></p>"}}, {:type=>:columns, :data=>{:columns=>[[{:type=>:image_link_with_description, :data=>{:image_src=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/22J1p6NSUAY1oTdslZbyNv/43bec672a33a8732a3ff803cd763e34e/child.jpeg", :link=>{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Set high expectations", :type=>:internal, :url=>"/guidance/set-high-expectations"}}, :description=>{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<p class=\"govuk-body\"><a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"/guidance/set-high-expectations\">Set high expectations</a></p>"}}}}], [{:type=>:image_link_with_description, :data=>{:image_src=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/3v03nBR3gJrfPl2mM50cSh/1b5fcf5d3cab1e3aef166acbae2eacfe/smiling-woman.jpeg", :link=>{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Promote good progress", :type=>:internal, :url=>"/guidance/promote-good-progress"}}, :description=>{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<p class=\"govuk-body\"><a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"/guidance/promote-good-progress\">Promote good progress</a></p>"}}}}]]}}, {:type=>:columns, :data=>{:columns=>[[{:type=>:image_link_with_description, :data=>{:image_src=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/3jAuIpjYNadASKJ8sSbiGX/9a10bb4ab7f4fb8f0f0a987a18428c57/woman-with-laptop.jpeg", :link=>{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Plan and teach well structured lessons", :type=>:internal, :url=>"/guidance/plan-and-teach-well-structured-lessons"}}, :description=>{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<p class=\"govuk-body\"><a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"/guidance/plan-and-teach-well-structured-lessons\">Plan and teach well structured lessons</a></p>"}}}}], [{:type=>:image_link_with_description, :data=>{:image_src=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/39APdN7OS30U4GzAG5WfNb/0252dbdf1b6160ec70edc224cdefd581/53224219_1489256524541522_4335915866861461131_n.jpg", :link=>{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Adaptive teaching", :type=>:internal, :url=>"/guidance/adaptive-teaching"}}, :description=>{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<p class=\"govuk-body\"><a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"/guidance/adaptive-teaching\">Adaptive teaching</a></p>"}}}}]]}}, {:type=>:columns, :data=>{:columns=>[[{:type=>:image_link_with_description, :data=>{:image_src=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/55FjGjLK7izPFskIjhl26G/6c85a9b2c35acdee2c6371ad19d524a0/lab-experiment.jpeg", :link=>{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Manage behaviour effectively", :type=>:internal, :url=>"/guidance/manage-behaviour-effectively"}}, :description=>{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<p class=\"govuk-body\"><a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"/guidance/manage-behaviour-effectively\">Manage behaviour effectively</a></p>"}}}}], [{:type=>:image_link_with_description, :data=>{:image_src=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/67lYH9JNpk3dweE5e1zx7P/96976b517f6044ffc58887bea77bff46/man-with-backpack.jpeg", :link=>{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Fulfil wider professional responsibilities", :type=>:internal, :url=>"/guidance/fulfil-wider-professional-responsibilities"}}, :description=>{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_content=>"<p class=\"govuk-body\"><a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"/guidance/fulfil-wider-professional-responsibilities\">Fulfil wider professional responsibilities</a></p>"}}}}]]}}, {:type=>:columns, :data=>{:columns=>[[{:type=>:image_link_with_description, :data=>{:image_src=>"//images.ctfassets.net/gfzscr0ovdsz/3MEU0iPuokRJSbBgaIeH5/e467ff02b5cd1e823d428f4484b00701/drawing-on-whiteboard.jpeg", :link=>{:type=>:link, :data=>{:text=>"Demonstrate good subject and curriculum knowledge", :type=>:internal, :url=>"/guidance/demonstrate-good-subject-and-curriculum-knowledge"}}, :description=>{:type=>:rich_text, :data=>{:html_cont